<li class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><span class="heap-of-link_name wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><a id="link-54080" class="track_this_link wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TOBn35rdQhY" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Heavenly, the band of retired OUP philosophy editor Peter Momtchiloff, has just released their first new single in 29 years</a></span> <span class="heap-of-link_description wp-dark-mode-bg-image">&#8212; check out &#8220;Portland Town&#8221; (via Eric Wiland)</span></li>
<li class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><span class="heap-of-link_name wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><a id="link-54079" class="track_this_link wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="https://amandaguinzburg.substack.com/p/diabolus-ex-machina" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">“What ultimately transpired is the closest thing to a personal episode of Black Mirror I hope to experience in this lifetime”</a></span> <span class="heap-of-link_description wp-dark-mode-bg-image">&#8212; enough of the time, the details must not matter&#8212;until they do</span></li>
<li class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><span class="heap-of-link_name wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><a id="link-54077" class="track_this_link wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-do-philosophy-of-physics-when-you-can-do-physics-itself" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">“The philosophy of physics is continuous with physics, insofar as it seeks to understand the structure of our best scientific theories of the world”</a></span> <span class="heap-of-link_description wp-dark-mode-bg-image">&#8212; a primer for nonspecialists on the question, &#8220;why *philosophy of* physics?&#8221;, from James Read</span></li>
<li class="wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><span class="heap-of-link_name wp-dark-mode-bg-image"><a id="link-54076" class="track_this_link wp-dark-mode-bg-image" href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/think/article/i-was-a-brain-in-a-vat/17FB89E0A1DE424BB65259AAE5EC28A1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">“I… [sued] the scientists who kept me envatted, performing experiment after experiment without my consent… The defense rests its case on—what else?—a philosophy argument…”</a></span> <span class="heap-of-link_description wp-dark-mode-bg-image">&#8212; a short story by Barbara Montero</span></li>
